JobPositionInformation.PositionTitle: Chef for Sushi og thai take away
JobPositionInformation.Purpose:
We are now hiring one more sushi and Wok  chef for our sushi amd thai take away shop. 
The person we are looking for must have experience in the sushi kitchen. It is important that you Can control the kitchen. we offer a dynamic and busy work place with at lot of good colleagues. It is important that you can work fast and keep the overview at busy times and make sure we have  everything ready for service. 
experience is a must. Good conditoons and high salary for the right person.
